。<ref>{{cite news| last =Dinoff| first =Dustin| title =Contemporary World Cinema: Film Diary: Citizen Duane| page =13| publisher =''[[Playback_(magazine)|Playback]]''| date =September 4, 2006| url =| accessdate = }}</ref>

